<item>
            <title>[LU-900] Using ncli.sh as configuration file without SRUN installed will cause test failure</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-900</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Cannot run test suites under lustre/tests with configuration file ncli.sh if there is no srun installed on test node.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The new added SRUN=${SRUN:-$(which srun 2&amp;gt;/dev/null} will cause error if there is no srun installed.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>lustre-master build #353</environment>
